name: Ready to fly
description:
I go through a solar gate. The mountain becomes a cloud in my landscape. That deity arose from the waters and invented the moon, the world and all the stars. Huiracocha "has always been", and created time by ordering the sun a cyclical movement over the terrestrial sky. I'm going through a new year with my friends, on a planet that still seems strange to me. I advance walking, running, flying. Other times I stop, lie down and wait for the sun to rise again from the sand on which I float. We keep creating, 2022. We keep creative and winged.

Dear friends and collectors, I hope this new year is filled with art, prosperity, and enjoyable learning. Thank you for support me on my journey. I wish you the best.
